td.div: English: A binary tree image made in Adobe Illustrator based on the original source of Binary tree.png, to replace that image. This is much like Binary search tree.svg, but with the elements shuffled to avoid insinuating that binary trees have to be in order.

tr.td: Own work based on: Binary tree.png
